This page describes how to install Gentoo Linux with Gnome 3 on a Gigabyte P27G v2 laptop.

== Preliminary assumptions ==

In this page, we assume we are using rEFInd as a bootmanager. rEFInd is able to detect kernels with EFI stub support. Please refer to the [http://www.rodsbooks.com/efi-bootloaders/refind.html  Managing EFI Boot Loaders for Linux:
Using rEFInd] page, to learn more about how to install rEFInd on your laptop.
